column2: SELECT ALL   m.OBJID AS AKARI_ID,   m.RA AS AKARI_RA,   m.DEC AS AKARI_DEC,      n.objid AS SDSS_ID,      o.z AS zph,   o.zErr AS e_zph,	      n.distance AS SEPARATION_AKARI_SDSS1#       into mydb.AKARIx3#SDSS1#_zsp from MyDB.akari AS m     OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n     LEFT JOIN Photo_zph AS o ON n.objid=o.objid
